<HEAD>Greek Soccer Fans Ransack Shop</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BELGRADE, Yugoslavia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Greek soccer fans ransacked a
duty-free shop at a Yugoslav border town after their team,
Olympiakos, lost a European Cup match this week, the state news
agency Tanjug reported.
   About 50 Greek fans stormed the shop at Bodogodica, near the
