<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   President Bush, anxious for money to launch the
war on drugs, says he is ready to deal with Senate Democrats seeking
to expand the program by $2.2 billion now and enlarge it in the
future.
   ``We're flexible in terms of the funding method,'' Bush said at a
